 *1346174301* Visualization of the structure of the Heart Sutra
 I had always thought that the structure of the Heart Sutra was interesting and wondered if I could do something good with it, but until now I had only been thinking about visualizing it as a two-dimensional image. I couldn't sleep and was in a daze when it suddenly occurred to me that it would be better to express it using sound and images as a moving image, so I wrote a storyboard for now, and while I was at it, I tried drawing a clean copy in Keynote and adding colors.
 
 Since there is no sound included yet, those who cannot recite the Heart Sutra may want to find an audio file on Youtube or Nico Nico Douga and flip through the pages in time with it.
 
